data.description: Welcome Home!! The impressive living space is truly exceptional, the open floor plan features a farmhouse interior and boasts an expansive living area with high ceilings, a large kitchen and an office. A foodie's dream kitchen it includes all stainless appliances with a gas stove and a double wall oven.  The large island has built-in cabinets for extra storage. Do not miss the walk in pantry off the kitchen. The main bedroom is off the living room and it boasts a large walk-in closet, the bathroom features a large  tile shower with a separate soaking tub. The inviting interior features hardwood and tile floors throughout the main level. When you follow the hidden stairs to the second floor you will find 2 bedrooms with full bathrooms attached to each room. The bonus room is tucked away on the 2nd floor as well. Do you love to entertain? If so this amazing backyard has it all. The screened in back porch leads you to the fire pit and onto the pool. The large pool deck gives you plenty of space to entertain and have fun in the sun. The new saltwater pool features a tanning ledge that is built into the pool. Let the animals roam in the fenced in backyard.
